        %p We're looking for a talented Android  Developer to join our team.
        %h2 Responsibilities:
        %ul
            %li You're in charge of the technical build of our cross-platform SDK.
            %li You work on building our iOS/Android utility apps for internal and external use.
            %li You follow the  platforms' guide lines and coding standards and see what’s on their roadmap.
            %li You write unit tests and perform regression tests for new and existing code.
            %li You generate appropriate documentation, from requirements and design documents to technical end-user tutorials.
