            %li You support end-users with their coding issues and are able to turn their feedback into improvements to the product.

    %section
        %h2 What we expect from you:
        %ul
            %li You have a mindset to design and build modular, reusable components and frameworks
            %li You see the tools you create as something you would love to use for yourself
            %li You thrive inside a dynamic organization exhibiting a high degree of uncertainty and love the freedom to be extremely creative
            %li You are capable of setting your own goals and work schedule and make sure your work aligns with that of others
            %li You are excited to join a team that is used to working remotely but know how to face the challenges this brings
            %li You are able to look beyond your own expertise and see the bigger picture of our products

    %section
        %h2 Qualifications
        %ul
            %li Bachelor’s or Master's Degree in Computer Science / Software Engineering
            %li Application development experience with either internal corporate apps or external consumer apps available to the popular app stores
            %li Demonstrated progressive experience successfully designing, delivering and maintaining  apps
            %li Must have demonstrated competency/expertise in Javascript, Java, MVC, design patterns and RESTful web services
            %li Ability to identify and resolve application defects
            %li Working knowledge of industry standard application design patterns
            %li Proven track record for deploying apps to app stores
            %li Working knowledge of application security issues
            %li Strong analytical and writing skills paired with a background in software development
            %li Fluent in English language both spoken and written

    %section
